title: [Bloodriven Village, Mark Alley]
description: The scent of decay is prolific in this narrow alleyway.  A pile of wet, rotting leaves is obviously partly responsible, though something hidden beneath it likely contributes.  A single broad cobweb connects two balconies on either side of the street, hanging only slightly higher than an average human.

The scent of cold air and decay is prolific in this narrow alleyway.  A pile of snow-layered, rotting leaves is obviously partly responsible, though something hidden beneath it likely contributes.  A single garland of unknown fauna connects two balconies on either side of the street, hanging only slightly higher than an average human.
